name: How It’s Like to Be a Cat
description:
It was a usual Monday for Frizzi the Cat. An accountant from Meowming, a state far from Mew York. That day he was scolded by his boss for not doing the cat calculation properly. 
“I was tired, boss.”, he said.
“Well, everyone is also tired!”
He stood in silence.
“Now we won’t be able to get extra Whizzkaz, and your bonus will be cut for this month.”, his boss left him in confusion.
He went home angrily but not forgetting to piss on his boss’s desk before leaving.
On his way home, he challenged all of the street cats for a battle, but no one dared to do that. They were afraid of his blobby belly.
Upon his arrival at home, he decided to watch his favorite series on Petflix and eat fresh tuna.
“Ah, who cares about work? I still have my human to feed me.”
He ended his day with an exercise to keep his blobby shape perfect.
“Tomorrow is my hairball day. Well, get ready for a new desk, boss.”
